max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 290px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲啤酒妹阿仪，图片来源：YSStudio@YouTube</p><figure class="picset picset--w5"><div class="picset-main"> </div></figure><div class="fancy-slider">YouTuber 「YS Studio 制作」（<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@YSStudio">@YSStudio</a> ）早前在 YouTube 上分享了部分游戏片段，片段中可见 AI 「日本阿仪」说话的确有些阿仪真人的神髓。</div><div> </div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220597" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/aiai00screenshot-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/aiai00screenshot-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/aiai00screenshot.png 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220598" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/aiai251screenshot-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/aiai251screenshot-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/aiai251screenshot.png 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></div><div style="text-align: center;">▲ YSStudio 上传的影片可见，「AI 阿仪」说话非常直接</div><div> </div><div> </div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220599" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708318897-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708318897-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708318897.jpg 1078w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div style="text-align: center;">▲游戏系统会利用「风趣」的语气提醒玩家课金（绿色框示）</div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220607" src="https://cdn.